    "description": "Complete API collection for the Kanban Board backend.\n\nEndpoints:\n- POST /auth/register\n- POST /auth/login\n- GET  /tasks\n- POST /tasks  (create / update / soft-delete)\n- GET  /health\n\nThe Login request automatically saves the returned JWT to the `token` environment variable. All task requests use it via `{{token}}`.\n\nRun in order: Register → Login → Task requests.",
